name: USD/AED
summary: The exchange rate between the United States Dollar (USD) and the United Arab Emirates Dirham (AED). It reflects how many AED can be purchased with one USD.

name: AED/AUD
summary: The exchange rate between the United Arab Emirates Dirham (AED) and the Australian Dollar (AUD). It reflects how many AUD can be purchased with one AED.

name: AED/BRX
summary: The exchange rate between the United Arab Emirates Dirham (AED) and a basket of currencies (BRX). It indicates how many units of the BRX currency basket are needed to purchase one AED. The rate reflects the relative value of the AED compared to the BRX currency basket.

name: AED/CAD
summary: The exchange rate between the United Arab Emirates Dirham (AED) and the Canadian Dollar (CAD). It reflects how many CAD can be purchased with one AED.

name: AED/CHF
summary: The exchange rate between the United Arab Emirates Dirham (AED) and the Swiss Franc (CHF). It reflects how many CHF can be purchased with one AED.
